<HEAD>Bush's Younger Brother To Work As Consultant</HEAD>
<DATELINE>SEOUL, South Korea (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   William Bush, the younger brother of
President Bush, has agreed to work as a consultant for the Samsung
group, one of South Korea's largest congolomerates, a company
spokesman said today.
   ``A basic agreement has been reached and both sides are working
on details, including terms of a contract,'' said the spokesman, who
