<HEAD>Plans Announced For Restoration Of Athens, New Acropolis Museum</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto ATH1</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ATHENS, Greece (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Millions of dollars worth of programs are
planned to restore and modernize Athens in full confidence Greece
will win the right to host the 1996 Olympics, Culture Minister
Meline Mercouri said Thursday.
   Premier Andreas Papandreou and Ms. Mercouri said at a news
