   Papandreou, 70, was accompanied by his 34-year-old live-in
girlfriend, Dimitra Liani.
   Scores of photographers pushed and shoved each other for position
to photograph Ms. Liani, who was wearing a bright pink spring outfit.
   Papandreou is seeking a divorce from his American-born wife, the
former Margaret Chant of Elmhurst, Ill. He smiled and waved to a
small group of supporters as he entered and left the press hall.
